hadiths[5]{hadithnumber,text}:
110,“The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) entered Mecca on the Day of Victory wearing a black turban.”
111,I saw a black turban on the head of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace).”
112,The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) addressed the people while wearing a black turban.”
113,"When the Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) donned a turban, he let his turban hang down between his shoulders.”"
114,“The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) addressed the people while wearing a turban that was dasma’ .
